#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_q1"
msgstr "Q. Can I directly use essays from Keydion commercially?"

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_a1"
msgstr "A. No. Only with the permission from the original author can one commercially use essays from Keydion. Keydion does not grant users the rights directly."

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_q2"
msgstr "Q. I am not from a school currently running Keydion. Can I submit?"

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_a2"
msgstr "A. Yes. Keydion is open to all schools and feel free to submit your essays to make a contribution to the academia and gain more attentions from others."

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_q3"
msgstr "Q. I want to join or collaborate with Keydion, how can I?"

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_a3"
msgstr "A. We always welcome either students or institutions to collaborate or join with us. Please contact us with the info given in the bottom of the main page."

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_q4"
msgstr "Q. My essay appeared in Keydion without permission, what shall I do?"

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_a4"
msgstr "A. Keydion absolutely prioritizes your rights. Please contact us ASAP with the info given in the bottom of the main page. We will try our best to provide assistance."

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_q5"
msgstr "Q. I found an issue of Keydion, what can I do?"

#: templates/FAQ.html
msgid "faq_a5"
msgstr "A. You may contact us with the info given in the bottom of the main page. Awards may be given."

#: templates/FAQ.html:155 templates/news.html:662 templates/search.html:66
msgid "Back to Home"
msgstr "Back to Home"

