#: templates/landing.html:1110
msgid "关于我们"
msgstr "About Us"

#: templates/landing.html:1111
msgid ""
"Keydion 是一个专为高中设计的学术资产平台。我们聚焦于学生的科研成果，包括 IA、EE、TOK "
"等项目。通过本平台，学生的研究成果将不再被忽视，而是被系统性地保存于 Keydion\n"
"            数据库中，供师生查阅与参考。同时，教师也可以更全面地了解本校科研项目的内容与整体质量。"
msgstr ""
"Keydion is an academic asset platform specifically designed for high "
"schools. We focus on students' research output, including IA, EE, TOK, "
"and other projects. Through this platform, students' research "
"achievements will no longer be overlooked but systematically preserved in"
" the Keydion database for reference by teachers and students. Moreover, "
"teachers can gain a more comprehensive understanding of the content and "
"overall quality of research projects at their school."

#: templates/landing.html:1113
msgid ""
"Keydion\n"
"            "
"同样致力于维护学术诚信，避免撞题以及学术不端误判。我们希望为每一所学校留存这些珍贵的学术成果，让优秀的学生研究经验得以传承，使学术探索不再只是一次性的作业，而成为可以持续积累与发展的知识资产。"
msgstr ""
"Keydion is also dedicated to maintaining academic integrity by preventing"
" topic overlap and avoiding false accusations of academic misconduct. We "
"hope to preserve these precious academic achievements for every school, "
"allowing outstanding student research experiences to be passed down, so "
"that academic exploration is no longer just a one-off assignment but a "
"knowledge asset that can be continuously accumulated and developed."

